high_descs: walk to face round wooden table
heat and remove tomato from microwave
Turn around and veer right to the round table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge, to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the wall, then turn left and go to the round table.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Go to the microwave on the counter behind you.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside and heat it, then take it out.
Turn right, move forward to the stove, then turn right and go straight ahead to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside, then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato in the fridge.
